claude-opus-4-8
,
claude-opus-4-7
,
claude-opus-4-6
Open-weight
GLM-5.2
,
Kimi-K2.7 Code
,
MiniMax-M3
Open-weight models are available through providers like
Baseten
,
Fireworks
,
OpenRouter
, and
Ollama
.
​
