Workflow:
Main agent creates high-level plan
Delegates data collection to data-collector
Passes results to data-analyzer
Sends insights to report-writer
Compiles final output
Each subagent works with clean context focused only on its task.
​
Context management
When you invoke a parent agent with
runtime context
, that context automatically propagates to all subagents. Each subagent run receives the same runtime context you passed on the parent
invoke
/
ainvoke
call.
This means tools running inside any subagent can access the same context values you provided to the parent:
Google
OpenAI
Anthropic
OpenRouter
Fireworks
Baseten
Ollama
